MEAN Project Notebook

1. Express command not working in terminal
   -when install Express.js, you need to use express-generator : sudo npm install -g express-generator

2. Installzation :
-install Python
-install Express
-install Node.js
-install Git
-$npm install -g bower
 $npm update -g bower
-$npm install -g grunt-cli
 $npm update -g grunt-cli
-$npm install -g yo
 $npm update -g yo
-$npm install -g generator-meanjs
 $npm update -g generator-meanjs

